        "save": "paralysis",
        "pattern": "transparent",
        "description": "<p>Sapient rats are too small to harm man-sized&nbsp;creatures individually. Instead, they may fight as packs, getting <strong>1 attack per 5 individuals</strong> in the pack.</p>\n<p>If a character is attacked by 10 or more sapient rats at once, he must also succeed in a saving throw versus Paralysis or fall to the ground under the writhing rodent horde. He may stand up the following round, but must make a new saving throw each time he is attacked by 10 or more rats. The character can take no other actions until he gets back on his feet.</p>",
